Create a folder in desktop:

folder : BlogPlatform

create a backend:

mkdir backend
cd backend
npm init -y
npm install express mongoose cors dotenv bcryptjs jsonwebtoken

npm install nodemon --save-dev

mkdir  server.js
mkdir models
mkdir routes
mkdir middleware
npm install dotenv



npm start

